1 Overview
**********

clamdscan-tools provides two command-line programs:

   • ‘clamdscan-progress’ runs scans with a progress indicator,
     resumable state files and configurable exclusions.
   • ‘clamdscan-watch’ shows or follows the logs produced by completed
     or active scans.

   The package is intended for Debian systems and integrates with the
standard filesystem layout for binaries, configuration, logs and Info
documentation.


