3.2 clamdscan-watch
===================

Synopsis:

     clamdscan-watch [OPTION]...

   Important options:

‘--log FILE’
     Display the selected log file.

‘--follow, -f’
     Follow the selected log file using semantics similar to ‘tail -f’.

‘-h, --help’
     Display built-in usage help.

   Examples:

     clamdscan-watch
     clamdscan-watch --follow
     clamdscan-watch --log /var/log/clamdscan-tools/scan_2026-03-23_12-00-00.log


